  <data name="ModuleHelp.Text" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>&lt;P&gt; &lt;h3&gt;&lt;b&gt;Steps to Configure the Module:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
	&lt;br/&gt;&lt;b&gt;Step1:&lt;/b&gt; Add one or more form categories on which fields will be grouped. (Go to page "Manage Categories") 
	&lt;br/&gt;&lt;b&gt;Step2:&lt;/b&gt; Add the desired form fields (Go to Page "Add/Edit Form Fields") 
	&lt;br/&gt;&lt;b&gt;Step3:&lt;/b&gt; Configure the email and Thank you page templates through the "Manage Workflow" Link. 	
	&lt;br/&gt;&lt;b&gt;Step4:&lt;/b&gt; Manage the look and feel of your form,Go to Link "Form Layout" 
	&lt;br/&gt;&lt;b&gt;Step5:&lt;/b&gt; If you are using multiple languages on your site, then you may want to enable multilanguage features from the Form layout page.
	&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Click module help to see these setup instructions again or refer to supplied PDF documentation for more details.&lt;/p&gt;</value>
  </data>
